{"tid":2276291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大總理及愛爾蘭總理搶閘祝賀拜登當選 期待與對方合作","createTime":"2020-11-07T18:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T05:01:40.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5268c84390edfe3799b99c553df66e22d02796ca","tid":2276291,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T18:00:18.000Z","msg":"華盛頓與紐約有人慶祝拜登當選 加拿大愛爾蘭亦祝賀<br />\n<br />\n美國多間傳媒推算民主黨總統候選人拜登勝出後，首都華盛頓與紐約都有拜登的支持者上街慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n在華盛頓，汽車響咹聲充斥街道，有人開香檳慶祝，幾百人聚集白宮附近一個廣場，一同歡呼、大笑和擊掌。而在紐約，民眾在家中露台拍掌歡呼，並敲打廚具。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大總理杜魯多祝賀拜登當選，期待與美國新政府合作，應對全球挑戰。拜登本身是愛爾蘭裔移民後代，愛爾蘭總理馬丁說，拜登是愛爾蘭的真正朋友，期待與拜登合作，亦歡迎他回家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558882-20201108.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558882-20201108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft2%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=8ee9f6c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558882-20201108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fe02e76c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558882-20201108.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5b435aa3ec7372b80c11ea5a3320fb0f4b3f8e5d","tid":2276291,"uid":12628,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T18:01:30.000Z","msg":"杜魯多條柒頭要柒幾多次先醒"},{"pid":"29af57ffaeea4999e78c8c6f676b70d17fbd0476","tid":2276291,"uid":33869,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"我都歡迎拜登回愛爾蘭嘅家，唔好返嚟美國"},{"pid":"d418dfac1d83bba5fb779b5776d26b8e9741ed6e","tid":2276291,"uid":295230,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"杜魯多你個黨既支持度跌落深淵啦，而且唔係新民主黨最後關頭保你，你落撚左台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /